    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Park Brake Indicator</title>
        <para>The PARK BRAKE indicator (see
            <hotlnk document="s04048_23.xml" xrefid="f0404820">FIGURE 20</hotlnk>) lights whenever the parking brake has
            been applied. A bulb check occurs each time the ignition switch is turned to the RUN position. The indicator
            will be turned on for about three seconds by the ESC; then will remain on (park brake is applied) until the
            park brake is released.
        </para>
    </svcsubproc>
